{"tid":2394311,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"20210204 我愛中間淳太","createTime":"2021-02-04T05:49:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-04T12:56:31.000Z","uid":11291,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9dec56785b6639b60403d04966c9353d982716c9","tid":2394311,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T05:49:20.000Z","msg":"今日ヒルナンテス！<br />\n<br />\n壽司朗除左壽司之外仲有咩食物係最出名<br />\n<br />\nA)甜品 B)拉麵<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uUysXrO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuUysXrO.png&h=084297b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全場得佢揀甜品，所以得佢一個答啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jULOGTv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjULOGTv.png&h=2b52eefa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住就講丸龜製麵<br />\n<br />\n有一條問題我cap唔切唔記得問咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但係又係淳太答啱<br />\n<br />\n最後一條問題<br />\n<br />\n日本（係日本，香港我唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）丸龜製麵除左蔥、薑、同埋炸嘢之外，仲有咩嘢係唔洗錢refill?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pxNUCtd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpxNUCtd.png&h=7e6335d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ELkZOCu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FELkZOCu.png&h=65c1bcb7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n答案係湯底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uEDpfhL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuEDpfhL.png&h=6e7a1d03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我淳答中曬問題 獎你由丸龜製麵鴨肉烏冬你食啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jp3pfid.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fjp3pfid.png&h=2930ce7e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"08e1a7c5ef8c6c611f8e227d9d5ded67c1b8ec35","tid":2394311,"uid":124310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T05:53:48.000Z","msg":"湯底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a34e22f8461ca6cbe374f15c633a194464be162b","tid":2394311,"uid":286155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T06:13:37.000Z","msg":"側邊淳太？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ea79ef57085a3b3576613aa7b6a10fd3eaba5e3","tid":2394311,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a34e22f8461ca6cbe374f15c633a194464be162b","tid":2394311,"uid":286155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T06:13:37.000Z","msg":"側邊淳太？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T06:15:58.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n圖一渣住A牌<br />\n同埋寫住出汁果個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33974ac6a6d5140dd5f5f6d2038d9b2c05917b59","tid":2394311,"uid":90460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7ea79ef57085a3b3576613aa7b6a10fd3eaba5e3","tid":2394311,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a34e22f8461ca6cbe374f15c633a194464be162b","tid":2394311,"uid":286155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T06:13:37.000Z","msg":"側邊淳太？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T06:15:58.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n圖一渣住A牌<br />\n同埋寫住出汁果個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji